title: Best REAL Hip-Hop and Rap Songs Of July 2013 [2-Disc]
description:
The latest monthly compilation from Real HipHopHead. A lot of dope and slept-on joints. The best Hip-Hop that dropped in this past month of July 2013. 2 Discs, 46 total tracks. Enjoy.

Artists featured include: Joey Bada$$, U-God, Jon Connor, KA, Alchemist, Reks, ANTHM, Skyzoo, Rapsody, Atmosphere and more.
